/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_0.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I offer it to you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1000.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And say, have they not risen?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1002.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as vultures gather round a dying ox?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1005.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they will come true,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1006.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and mine is the song of a people that is doomed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1008.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of these other words I will speak in their place.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1011.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went to my mother.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1013.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently she raised herself from the ground and sat up with her hands over her face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The blood from the wound the stick had made ran down her face on to her breast,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he was thrown in with men who,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1021.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She sat for a long while thus,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the child cried,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1025.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the cow lowed to be milked,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1026.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wiped up the blood with the grass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1029.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last she took her hands away and spoke to me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1031.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she said,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1032.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have dreamed a dream.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1033.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he was grown like a giant.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1035.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his eyes blazed like the lightning,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He caught up people after people in his hands and tore them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for thirty or forty years,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1041.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Before him was the green of summer,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1043.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw our people, Mopo;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1045.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they were many and fat,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1046.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their hearts laughed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1048.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the men were brave,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1049.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the girls were fair;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1050.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I counted their children by the hundreds.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1052.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw them again, Mopo.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1054.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thousands of bones tumbled together in a rocky place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1058.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1059.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|stood over the bones and laughed till the earth shook.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_106.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had been intimately acquainted with the Zulu people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1062.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You alone were left of our people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1064.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and with you came others,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1065.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You stabbed him with a little spear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1067.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he fell down and grew small again;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1070.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he fell down and cursed you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your sister-and he died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1074.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we rose and went home.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1076.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I held my peace, for I was afraid, very much afraid.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1081.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and died quickly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1083.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then my mother fell down and died,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1085.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I cried very much,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1087.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I loved her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1088.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and it was dreadful to see her cold and stiff,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_109.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with their history,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1091.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with not a word to say however loudly I called to her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1095.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, they buried my mother, and she was soon forgotten.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1099.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I only remembered her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_11.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a song has been sung in my ears of how first you mastered this people of the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and their customs.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1100.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|nobody else did-not even Baleka,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for she was too little-and as for my father he took another young wife and was content.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_111.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|From these he heard many tales and traditions,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1110.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that I was unhappy,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1112.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for my brothers did not love me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1113.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because I was much cleverer than they,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1115.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and was swifter in running;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1117.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so they poisoned the mind of my father against me and he treated me badly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1123.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we were both lonely,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1124.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and she clung to me like a creeper to the only tree in a plain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1128.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and though I was young,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1129.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that to be wise is to be strong,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1132.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|yet he whose mind directs the battle is greater than he who kills.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I saw that the witch-finders and the medicine-men were feared in the land,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_114.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|are rarely told nowadays,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1141.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that everybody looked up to them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|even when they had only a stick in their hands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1146.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|ten men armed with spears would fly before them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I learned the arts of the medicine-men.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1152.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I made sacrifices,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I did all those things of which you have heard,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1156.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I learned much;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for there is wisdom in our magic as well as lies-and you know it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in time to come may cease to be told altogether.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1162.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1163.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|else you had not come here to ask me about your lost oxen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1167.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So things went on till I was twenty years of age-a man full grown.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1172.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|By now I had mastered all I could learn by myself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I joined myself on to the chief medicine-man of our tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who was named Noma.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was old, had one eye only, and was very clever.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1184.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Of him I learned some tricks and more wisdom,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1188.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but at last he grew jealous of me and set a trap to catch me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|now that nation has been destroyed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a rich man of a neighbouring tribe had lost some cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and came with gifts to Noma praying him to smell them out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1199.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then the headman grew angry and demanded back his gifts;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1203.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and hot words passed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, for I feared that blood would be shed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1208.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"You are nothing but a boy,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_121.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the chief aim of its white rulers is to root out the warlike spirit for which it was remarkable,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Can a boy have wisdom?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"That shall soon be known,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1214.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, taking the bones in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1217.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|throwing them something as we throw dice.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1219.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Leave the bones alone!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1221.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We will ask nothing more of our snakes for the good of this son of a dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1224.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"He shall throw the bones,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1226.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he lifted his spear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I made haste to begin; I threw the bones.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The headman sat on the ground before me and answered my questions.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1236.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father-how sometimes the witch-doctor has knowledge of where the lost things are,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for our ears are long,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as but the other day it told me of your oxen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, in this case, my snake stood up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew nothing of the man's cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1251.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and told them to him one by one,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1253.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and how one of them had fallen into a stream and lay there on its back drowned,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1257.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the man was pleased,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1258.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and said that if my sight was good,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he found the cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1262.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the gifts should be taken from Noma and given to me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1265.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he asked the people who were sitting round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1268.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there were many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1269.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if this was not just.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to replace it by a spirit of peaceful progress.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yes, yes,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1271.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they said, it was just, and they would see that it was done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1275.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He knew that I had made a true divination, and he was very angry.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1280.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was a big matter:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1282.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the herd of cattle were many,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1283.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then all men would think me the greater wizard.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now it was late,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1287.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the moon had not yet risen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1290.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that he went away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1291.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I too went into my hut and lay down to sleep.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1295.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Suddenly I awoke, feeling a weight upon my breast.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1298.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I fell back again and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_130.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|perhaps the most wonderful that the world has seen,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the moon lay low on the sky like a ball of fire far away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1304.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was seated across me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in his hand was a knife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1308.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he hissed into my ear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1310.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Very well, now I will show you how I serve such puppies.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1313.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that you cannot squeal,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1315.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I will cut you to pieces slowly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in the morning I will tell the people that the spirits did it because you lied.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1323.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Next, I will take off your arms and legs.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, yes, I will make you like a stick!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1328.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I will
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1329.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he began driving in the knife under my chin.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_133.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|is already a thing of the past;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1332.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Mercy, my uncle,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1334.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Will you do this?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he asked, still pricking me with the knife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1337.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Will you get up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1338.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and hide them there?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_134.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|building it up from the smallest beginnings.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1340.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he named a secret valley that was known to very few.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1343.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If you do that, I will spare you and give you three of the cows.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1348.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|by my father's spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1350.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will find a way to kill you!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1352.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Certainly I will do it, my uncle,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1353.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1354.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Why did you not trust me before?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1356.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Had I known that you wanted to keep the cattle,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1359.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would never have smelt them out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1361.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"You are not so wicked as I thought,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1363.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Get up, then, and do my bidding.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1365.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You can be back here two hours after dawn.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1368.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I got up,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1369.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thinking all the while whether I should try to spring on him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_137.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When he appeared at the commencement of this century,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1373.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I was without arms, and he had the knife;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1376.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|also if,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1377.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I prevailed and killed him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1378.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I made another plan.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1380.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would go and find the cattle in the valley where I had smelt them out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1384.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I would not bring them to the secret hiding-place.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1388.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all the people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He had not been a witch-doctor till he grew old for nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1393.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He had planted me by him like a tree,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1396.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he meant to keep me clipped like a bush.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1399.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I had grown tall and overshadowed him;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_140.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it was as the ruler of a single small tribe;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1402.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went to the corner of my hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1404.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Noma watching me all the while,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1406.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I started through the moonlight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1408.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I began to run,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1410.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|singing to myself as I went,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to frighten away the ghosts,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1413.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For an hour I travelled swiftly over the plain,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1416.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till I came to the hillside where the bush began.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here it was very dark under the shade of the trees,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_142.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when he fell,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1422.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I sang louder than ever.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1424.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last I found the little buffalo path I sought, and turned along it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1429.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently I came to an open place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in the year eighteen twenty eight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|where the moonlight crept in between the trees.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1434.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knelt down and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1436.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sometimes whispering and sometimes talking out loud.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1440.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Here the trail of the cattle was broad:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1442.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they had broken down the ferns with their feet and trampled the grass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1446.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently I came to a pool.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1448.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And there at the edge of the pool floated the drowned ox,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as he is called also,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1453.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stepped forward and looked round.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1455.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My eye caught something;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1456.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I looked, one of them snorted, rose and shook the dew from his hide.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_146.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and in his march to power he had slaughtered more than a million human beings.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1461.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He seemed big as an elephant in the mist and twilight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1464.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as Noma had bid me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1466.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I would not do this.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1468.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and tell all men that Noma was a thief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1470.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I sat, I heard a noise, and looked up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1473.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|came a crowd of men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1475.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and leading them was Noma,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1477.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and by his side the headman who owned the cattle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1480.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I rose and stood still, wondering;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1482.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but as I stood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1483.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they ran towards me shouting and waving sticks and spears.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1487.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|screamed Noma.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1488.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he is!-the clever boy whom I have brought up to bring shame on me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1493.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What did I tell you?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1494.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Did I not tell you that he was a thief?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1496.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes-yes!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1497.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he is stealing the cattle!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1499.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He knew where they were all the time,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1501.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and now he is taking them away to hide them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1504.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They would be useful to buy a wife with,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1506.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my clever boy?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1507.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I understood now, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so no more need be said of them here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1510.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My heart went mad in me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1511.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|everything began to swim round,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1513.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a red cloth seemed to lift itself up and down before my eyes.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1518.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have always seen it thus when I was forced to fight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1521.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I screamed out one word only,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1524.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I yelled again, and rushed on at the headman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1526.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He got up his shield,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1528.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I knocked it down upon his head,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_153.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|has been to convey,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1530.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and over he rolled senseless.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1532.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Whether he lived or died I do not know, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1535.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but his head being of the thickest, I think it likely that he lived.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in a narrative form,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1540.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the people stood astonished,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1542.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I turned and fled like the wind.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1544.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|throwing spears at me and trying to cut me off.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1547.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went like the wind;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1549.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and presently the sound of their chase grew fainter and fainter,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_155.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to make accessible,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1553.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at last I was out of sight and alone.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1556.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I went and hid in a patch of reeds down by a swamp.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1560.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|All day long I lay there thinking.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1562.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What was I to do?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1564.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I was a jackal without a hole.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1566.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If I went back to my people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1568.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|certainly they would kill me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_157.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in a popular shape,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1570.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whom they thought a thief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1571.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I did not wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1573.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though my heart was sad.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1575.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the boy to whom I had given the cup of water long ago.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I had heard of him: his name was known in the land;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|incidents of history which are now,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1582.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|already the air was big with it;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1584.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the very trees and grass spoke it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1586.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The words he had said and the vision that my mother had seen were beginning to come true.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1592.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that nobody could find them any more.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1594.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I thought to myself that I would arise and go to him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1598.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Perhaps he would kill me; well, what did it matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_16.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And when they grew weary,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_160.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|only to be found in a few scarce works of reference,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1602.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Certainly I should be killed if I stayed here.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1604.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, I would go.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1605.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But now my heart pulled another way.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1608.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There was but one whom I loved in the world-it was my sister Baleka.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1613.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My father had betrothed her to the chief of a neighbouring tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1617.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I knew that this marriage was against her wish.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1620.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Perhaps my sister would run away with me if I could get near her to tell her that I was going.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1624.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I would try-yes, I would try.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1627.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I waited till the darkness came down,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1630.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I was very hungry,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1631.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Some of my people were seated outside of a hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1634.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|talking together over a fire.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1636.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I crept near, silently as a snake, and hid behind a little bush.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|rarely consulted,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1641.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew that they could not see me outside the ring of the firelight,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1645.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I wanted to hear what they said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1647.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I guessed, they were talking of me and called me many names.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_165.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It will be obvious that such a task has presented difficulties,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1652.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Just then a dog that was lying by the fire got up and began to sniff the air.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1656.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could not see what dog it was-indeed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1659.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is what comes of want of experience, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1663.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The dog sniffed and sniffed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then he began to growl,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1666.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|looking always my way,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1668.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I grew afraid.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1669.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"What is the dog growling at?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1671.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said one man to another.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1673.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But the other man was taking snuff and did not like to move.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1676.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Let the dog go and see for himself,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1679.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered, sneezing,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_168.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and think with the mind and speak with the voice of a Zulu of the old regime.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1680.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"what is the good of keeping a dog if you have to catch the thief?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1683.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the first man to the dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1685.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he ran forward, barking.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1687.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as I lay not knowing what to do,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1690.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|stopped barking,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1691.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I whispered to him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1692.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he lay down by my side.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1694.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Where has that dog gone now?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1696.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the first man.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1698.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he stops barking suddenly and does not come back?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_17.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|did you not stand and say,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1700.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"We will see,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1701.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the other, rising, a spear in his hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1705.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now once more I was terribly afraid,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1708.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or I must run for my life again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1710.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But as I sprang up to run,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1712.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|a big black snake glided between the men and went off towards the huts.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1717.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They jumped aside in a great fright,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1719.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then all of them turned to follow the snake,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1722.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying that this was what the dog was barking at.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1725.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1726.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which without any doubt took the shape of a snake to save my life.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_173.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|their details have, therefore, been suppressed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1731.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At first I thought that I would kill him, lest he should betray me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1735.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he sat down upon the ground wagging his tail,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1738.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I thought that I would take my chance, and we went on together.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1742.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This was my purpose:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1744.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|would be empty,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1745.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I came to the reed fence that surrounded the huts.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1748.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Nobody was to be seen at the gate,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Still much remains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1750.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which was not shut with thorns as usual.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1753.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was my duty to close it, and I had not been there to do so.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1757.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bidding the dog lie down outside,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1759.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stepped through boldly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1761.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|reached the door of my hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1763.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and listened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1764.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was empty; there was not even a breath to be heard.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1767.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which was so nicely carved that I did not like to leave it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_177.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|may be invited to leave this book unread.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1771.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Soon I found them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1773.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I felt about for my skin rug,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1775.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and as I did so my hand touched something cold.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1779.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I started, and felt again.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1781.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was a man's face-the face of a dead man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1785.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I was frightened,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1786.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when suddenly I heard the voices of women talking outside the door of the hut.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|indeed nearly all,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1791.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew the voices;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1792.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I was in a trap indeed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1794.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Presently she was in,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1796.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she began to make lamentations and to call down curses on me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1801.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she did not know that I was listening.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1803.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now that the woman was there I was not so much afraid of the dead man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1807.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he had been a great cheat;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1809.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I thought I would make him cheat for the last time.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_181.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for the reason given,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1813.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I placed my hands beneath his shoulders and pushed him up so that he sat upon the ground.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1818.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The woman heard the noise and made a sound in her throat.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_182.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that he prophesied of the coming of the white man after receiving his death wounds.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1822.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Can you not let me be at peace, even now when I am dead?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1826.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|drew in her breath to shriek aloud.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1829.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then I must teach you silence.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1831.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then her senses left her,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1833.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and whether she ever found them again I do not know.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1836.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At least she grew quiet for that time.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1839.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and worth three oxen-and I fled,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1842.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my father,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1843.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|was two hundred paces away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1845.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I must go thither,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1846.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because a man was always on guard there.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1849.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I knew on which side of the hut it was her custom to lie,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1852.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and where her head would be.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1854.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I lay down on my side and gently,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1857.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|began to bore a hole in the grass covering of the hut.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1860.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It took a long while,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1862.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for the thatch was thick,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1863.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but at last I was nearly through it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1866.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for it came into my mind that Baleka might have changed her place,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_187.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it is impossible to speak so certainly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1870.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I might wake the wrong girl.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1872.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I almost gave it over,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1874.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thinking that I would fly alone,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1876.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when suddenly I heard a girl wake and begin to cry on the other side of the thatch.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1880.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"that is Baleka, who weeps for her brother!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1883.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I put my lips where the thatch was thinnest and whispered:-
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1887.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Say not a word, but rise.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1889.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Come out of the hut, bringing your skin blanket.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_189.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he cannot discover any confirmation of it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1892.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she did not shriek, as most girls would have done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1895.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she understood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1896.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she rose and crept from the hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1898.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|her blanket in her hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_19.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|pointing towards the ocean:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1900.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she whispered, as we met.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1901.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Surely you will be killed!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1903.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And then I told her of the plan which I had made.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1906.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Will you come with me?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1907.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, when I had done,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1909.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She thought awhile, then she said,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1912.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I love you alone among our people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1915.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though I believe that this will be the end of it-that you will lead me to my death.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1919.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I did not think much of her words at the time,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|these kings undoubtedly put their soldiers to many tests of equal severity.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1922.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but afterwards they came back to me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1925.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we slipped away together,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1927.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as we were afraid of being seen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1929.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Towards the afternoon we heard voices,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1931.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1932.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At night we travelled again;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1934.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we were met by an old woman,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1936.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who looked oddly at us but said nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1938.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After that we pushed on day and night,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1941.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we knew that the old woman would tell the pursuers if she met them;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1945.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and so indeed it came about.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1947.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and saw that they had been trampled down.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1949.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Among the broken mealies we found the body of a very old man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1953.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We wondered at this, and went on a little way.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1956.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Afterwards we became used to such sights.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1959.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|scores of them-old men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Umbopo, or Mopo, as he is named in this tale, actually lived.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1961.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|young men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1962.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|little babies at the breast-there they lay among the burnt huts,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1966.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Red was the earth with their blood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1968.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and red they looked in the red light of the setting sun.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1972.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was as though all the land had been smeared with the bloody hand of the Great Spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1977.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Baleka saw it and began to cry;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1980.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she was weary,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1981.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|poor girl,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1982.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we had found little to eat,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1984.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|only grass and green corn.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1986.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"An enemy has been here,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1987.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and as I spoke I thought that I heard a groan from the other side of a broken reed hedge.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1992.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I went and looked.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1994.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There lay a young woman:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1995.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she was badly wounded, but still alive, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_1999.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|A little way from her lay a man dead,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you knew his brother Panda and his captains,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_20.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Kill me if you wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2001.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and before him several other men of another tribe:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2004.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he had died fighting.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2006.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|another, a little one, lay on her body.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2009.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I looked at the woman,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_201.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he disappears from the scene,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2010.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she groaned again,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2011.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|opened her eyes and saw me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2013.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and that I had a spear in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2016.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Kill me quickly!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2017.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2018.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Have you not tortured me enough?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2020.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said that I was a stranger and did not want to kill her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Then bring me water,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2025.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There were bodies in it,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2027.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I dragged them out,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2028.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and her strength came back a little-the water gave her life.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_203.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but it is not accurately known whether he also went
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2032.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"How did you come to this?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2033.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2034.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes, I woke up to hear the sound of killing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I was sleeping by my husband,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2039.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with him who lies there,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2040.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the children.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2042.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We all ran out.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2043.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My husband had a spear and shield.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2045.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was a brave man.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2046.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he died bravely:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2048.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he killed three of the Zulu devils before he himself was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2052.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and stabbed me till they thought that I was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2054.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Afterwards, they went away.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2056.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She stopped, gave a great cry, and died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which has been considerably varied to suit the purposes of this romance.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2060.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|My sister wept at the sight, and I too was stirred by it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2064.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I thought to myself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2065.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If he is not evil such things would not happen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2068.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That is how I thought then, my father; now I think differently.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2072.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I know that we had not found out the path of the Great Spirit,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2076.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is all.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2077.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I was a chicken in those days, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2080.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|afterwards I got used to such sights.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2082.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we had to look at the water to see if it was clean before we drank.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2086.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|People learned how to die then and not make a noise about it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2091.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|What does it matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2092.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They would have been dead now anyway.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2094.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It does not matter; nothing matters, except being born.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2098.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That is a mistake, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_210.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Among the Zulus and Amatongas.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2100.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but we could not sleep,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2102.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the ghosts of the dead people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2104.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|moving about and calling to each other.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2106.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was natural that they should do so;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2109.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|men were looking for their wives, and mothers for their children.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2112.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But we were afraid that they might be angry with us for being there,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so we clung together and trembled in each other's arms.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and towards morning their cries grew fainter.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I heard a story the other day,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2122.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When the first light came we rose and picked our way through the dead down to the plain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and sometimes we came to the body of a warrior who had been killed because his wounds prevented him from marching farther.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_213.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he says,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2134.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for after what we had seen I grew afraid lest he should kill us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2138.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we had nowhere to turn,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2139.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so I said that we would walk along till something happened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_214.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I might have worked up into a first-class sensational novel.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2143.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we grew faint with hunger and weariness,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for then there would be no more trouble.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2147.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So we sat down by a spring.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But I did not wish to die yet,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and it would have been well to do so.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and presently I heard him spring at something and the sound of struggling.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2158.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as big as himself,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2159.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that was asleep in it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2161.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for here was food.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2162.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we took bits of the flesh,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for we had no fire to cook them with.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2166.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is not nice to eat uncooked flesh,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2169.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but we were so hungry that we did not mind,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2172.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the food refreshed us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2174.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|When we had eaten what we could,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2176.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we rose and washed ourselves at the spring;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2179.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|on the crest of the hill,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_218.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is the story that has been woven into the plot of this book.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|about ten spear-throws away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2183.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|was a party of six armed men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2185.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|people of my own tribe-children of my father Makedama-who still pursued us to take us or kill us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2192.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They saw us-they raised a shout, and began to run.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2196.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now the land lay thus.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2197.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which twisted through the plain like a great and shining snake.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_22.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I tell you that for every drop of my blood a hundred avengers shall rise from yonder sea!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2201.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|On the other side the ground rose again,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we did not know what was beyond,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We ran for the river-where else were we to run?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And after us came the warriors.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They gained on us;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2212.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they were strong, and they were angry because they had come so far.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2216.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Run as we would, still they gained.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2218.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we neared the banks of the river; it was full and wide.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_222.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it was told to Mister Leslie by the Zulu who performed the feat and thereby won a wife.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2222.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Above us the waters ran angrily,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2224.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|between the two a deep pool,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|where the water was quiet but the stream strong.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2230.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|my brother, what shall we do?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2231.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"There is this to choose,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2234.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|perish on the spears of our people or try the river.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2237.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Easier to die by water than on iron,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2240.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now may our snakes look towards us and the spirits of our fathers be with us!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2245.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At the least we can swim.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2247.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And I led her to the head of the pool.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which I held in my teeth-and we plunged in,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2252.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|wading as far as we could.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2254.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we were up to our breasts;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2256.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|now we had lost the earth and were swimming towards the middle of the river,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2260.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you swim, do you?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Well, you will drown;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2262.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if we must run over the edge of the world after you we will catch you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2266.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|which fell between us like a flash of light.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2269.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|While he spoke we swam hard, and now we were in the current.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_227.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Also the writer's thanks are due to his friends,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2273.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It swept us downwards, but still we made way, for we could swim well.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2278.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was just this:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2279.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if we could reach the bank before we were swept into the rapids we were safe;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2284.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if not, then-good night!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2286.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now we were near the other side, but, alas!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2289.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|we were also near the lip of the foaming water.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|late Zulu border agent,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2292.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We strained, we struggled.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2294.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Baleka was a brave girl, and she swam bravely;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2298.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but the water pushed her down below me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2300.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I could do nothing to help her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2302.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I could not go back.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2303.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She grasped him by the tail with her right hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2306.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he put out his strength-he was very strong.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_231.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for much information given to him in bygone years by word of mouth,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2310.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She too struck out with her feet and left hand,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2313.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and slowly-very slowly-drew near.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2316.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She caught it with her left hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Already her feet were over the brink of the rapids,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2321.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and we brought her safe into the shallows,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2324.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and from the shallows to the bank,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2326.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there she fell gasping.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2328.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now when the soldiers on the other bank saw that we had crossed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2332.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|they shouted threats at us,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2334.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then ran away down the bank.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2335.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said:
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2336.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Ah, let me die!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2337.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2339.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For two hours we walked,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2340.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till at last we came to the crest of the rise,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2343.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2344.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Yes, brother,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2345.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2346.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but what waits us there?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2347.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Death is behind us and before us-we are in the middle of death.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_235.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|formerly treasurer to the Government of Natal,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2352.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then we looked back, and lo!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2354.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Again we ran, but now we were weak, and they gained upon us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2358.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then once more I thought of the dog.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2360.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was fierce and would tear any one on whom I set him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2364.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I called him and told him what to do,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2366.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He understood,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2367.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and flew towards the soldiers growling,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2369.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his hair standing up on his spine.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2372.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but he jumped round them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2373.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|At last a man hit him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2375.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he sprang up and seized the man by the throat.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2378.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There he clung,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2379.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|man and dog rolling over and over together,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_238.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whose compilation,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2383.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|till the end of it was that they both died.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2386.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he was a dog!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2387.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|We do not see such dogs nowadays.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2389.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Meanwhile, we had been running.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_239.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"The Annals of Natal,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2391.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and there was something going on inside it;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2394.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|leaving the dead dog and the dying man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2396.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|came after us swiftly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2397.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I saw that they must catch us before we reached the gate,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_240.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Watcher of the Fords,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2401.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then a thought came into my head.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2403.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I had brought her here, I would save her life if I could.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2406.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said, dropping behind.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2408.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now she was almost blind with weariness and terror,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2411.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I was about to fight four men till I was killed.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2415.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and all fear left me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2417.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The men were running,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2418.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|two and two,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with the length of a spear throw between them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_242.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|is an historical weapon,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2422.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of the first pair one was five or six paces in front of the other.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2427.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This man shouted out loud and charged me, shield and spear up.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He was an arbitrary person, for
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but I was crafty and he was overbold.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2434.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|On he came.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2435.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stood waiting for him till he drew back the spear to stab me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2439.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then suddenly I dropped to my knees and thrust upward with all my strength,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2444.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|beneath the rim of his shield,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2446.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he also thrust,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2447.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but over me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2448.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his spear only cutting the flesh of my shoulder-see!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2453.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|here is its scar; yes, to this day.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2456.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it went home; it ran through and through his middle.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|no matter what was discussed in our village,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2460.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He rolled over and over on the plain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2462.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The dust hid him;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2464.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|leaving nothing but a little bit of stick in my hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2466.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then in the darkness I saw a light.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2469.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I fell on to my hands and knees and flung myself over sideways.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2474.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|lifting his feet from beneath him.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2476.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Down he came heavily.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2478.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Before he had touched the ground I was off it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_248.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he would bring it to a conclusion with a stick.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2480.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|His spear had fallen from his hand.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2483.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I stooped, seized it, and as he rose I stabbed him through the back.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2488.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was all done in the shake of a leaf, my father;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2491.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in the shake of a leaf he also was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2494.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|About a hundred paces from me Baleka was staggering along with her arms out like one who has drunk too much beer.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_250.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But he made a good end;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2502.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But then her strength left her altogether.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2504.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yes!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2505.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|there she fell senseless, and I stood by her.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2509.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I should have been killed,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2510.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|had not this chanced,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2511.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|since the other two men,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2513.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|having stayed one instant by their dead fellows,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2516.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and through it ran a party of soldiers dragging a prisoner by the arms.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_252.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for when the Zulu soldiers attacked him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2521.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|After them walked a great man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2523.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who wore a leopard skin on his shoulders,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2526.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and was laughing,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2527.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and after them again came a company of warriors.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2530.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"We are of the children of Makedama,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2532.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but now two of us are dead at their hands,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2534.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and others lie dead along the road.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2536.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Suffer that we slay them.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2538.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the soldiers;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2539.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|ask too that he suffer you should not be slain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_254.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he killed no less than twenty of them with the Watcher,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2542.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Just then the tall chief saw blood and heard words.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2546.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He stalked up;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2548.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and his chest was big as the chests of two;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2551.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his face was fierce and beautiful,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2553.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he asked, frowning.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2555.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|answered the captain of the soldiers,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2557.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bending himself double before him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2559.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2560.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said those men of my people who sought to kill us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2563.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he answered, then spoke once more to the captain.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2567.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|let themselves be blinded and turned loose to seek their way home,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_257.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the spears stuck in him
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2572.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because they have dared to lift a spear within the Zulu gates.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2576.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now praise on, my children!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2578.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|while the soldiers murmured,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_258.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as thick as reeds in a morass.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2580.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|his justice is bright and terrible like the sun! But the two men of my people cried out in fear,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2587.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Cut out their tongues also,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2589.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|There lies the girl.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2590.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She is asleep and helpless.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2592.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|you hesitate?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2593.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Take these men, smear them with honey, and pin them over ant-heaps;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2598.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But first kill these two hunted jackals,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_260.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|This man's strength was so great that he could kill a leopard
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2601.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They seem tired and doubtless they long for sleep.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2605.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then for the first time I spoke, for the soldiers drew near to slay us.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2609.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I broke in,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2610.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It was I who gave thee a gourd of water many years ago,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2614.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when we were both little.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2615.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|vowing that thou wouldst protect me and never do me harm.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2619.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I have come, bringing my sister with me;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2622.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and now, I pray thee, do not eat up the words of long ago.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2625.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|As I spoke,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2627.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and he listened earnestly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2628.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2629.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Welcome, Mopo!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2630.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But of thy sister I said nothing.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2633.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|should she not be slain when I swore vengeance against all thy tribe,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2637.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|save thee alone?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2638.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered, boldly;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_264.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|with his hands only,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2640.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"also because I love her, and ask her life as a boon!"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2644.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And they did so, showing her face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2646.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|said the chief.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2647.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I grant thee the boon.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2649.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|So I sat down and told him all.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_265.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It has been little if at all exaggerated.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2651.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Nor did he grow weary of listening.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2654.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when I had done,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2655.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if he had still been alive,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2657.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then he spoke to the captain of the soldiers.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2659.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I take back my words,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2661.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|he said.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2662.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|One shall die and the other shall go free.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2665.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|here, Mopo, we have a man who has proved himself a coward.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2669.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The man fought well-he slew three of my people.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2673.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then this dog was afraid to meet him face to face.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2677.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and afterwards he stabbed the woman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2679.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now I will do him honour.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_268.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and to take the form of a young maiden,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2681.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will send back the other pig to the sty with a message.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2685.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Choose, children of Makedama, which of you will live.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2688.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now the two men of my tribe were brothers,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2691.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and loved one another,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2692.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and each of them was willing to die that the other might go free.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2696.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|saying that they would fight the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2698.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"What, is there honour among pigs?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_27.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|in fact an angel.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2701.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I will settle it.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2702.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I throw it into the air;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2704.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if the blade falls uppermost the tall man shall go free;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2708.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if the shaft falls uppermost, then life is to the short one, so!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_271.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|She is said to appear to some chosen person,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2713.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And he sent the little spear whirling round and round in the air.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2717.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Every eye watched it as it wheeled and fell.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2720.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The haft struck the ground first.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2722.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and say to him,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2724.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|To-day the dog of thy son Mopo howls upon the roof of thy hut.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2729.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The saying conveyed a threat to be appreciated by every Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2733.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|shook his brother by the hand,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2734.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bearing the words of evil omen.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2737.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|bidding them fight.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2738.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|when they had praised the prince they fought fiercely,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_274.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to whom she imparts some revelation;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2742.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the end of it was that the man of my people conquered the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2746.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But as soon as he had found his breath again he was set to run for his life,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2751.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and after him ran five chosen men.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2754.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it came about that he outran them,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2756.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for I think that he bade the men who hunted him to make speed slowly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_276.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whatever that revelation may be,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_2761.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that he would always save the life of a brave man if he could do so without making his word nothing.
