/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3023.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I will tell you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3024.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He spoke to them gently, gently.
