/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3037.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That is how we dealt with cowards in those days, my father.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_304.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|deserting them for the time being,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3041.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|If ten came against him, still he did not turn his back.
