/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3047.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|That fight was but one war out of many.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3050.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but with victory and countless cattle.
