/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3114.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|so that he might be sure that it was dead.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3116.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and would not her child be of my own blood?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3119.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it must be so,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3120.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|if we dared to disobey,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3122.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Better that an infant should die than that we should become food for jackals.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3127.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the place of the king's wives,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3129.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but when they saw me they rose and went away,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3132.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for it was not lawful that they should stay where I was.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3136.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thus I was left alone with my sister.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3138.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and I did not speak,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_314.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Briefly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3140.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|though I saw by the heaving of her breast that she was weeping.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3144.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said at length;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3145.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your sorrow will soon be done.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3147.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered, lifting her head,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3149.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|it will be but begun.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_315.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|or the spirit of an ancestor,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3151.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Oh, cruel man!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3152.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I know the reason of your coming.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3154.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|You come to murder the babe that shall be born of me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3157.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is the king's word, woman.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3159.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It is the king's word, and what is the king's word?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_316.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to that of a god.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3161.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Have I, then, naught to say in this matter?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3164.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Have I not loved you, Mopo?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3166.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Did I not flee with you from our people and the vengeance of our father?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3170.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and would have caused you to be slain had I not pleaded for you and called his oath to mind?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3175.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And thus you pay me: you come to kill my child, my first-born child!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_318.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|In the case of an able and highly intelligent person like the Mopo of this story,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3180.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"It is the king's word, woman,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3182.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|turning her face to the wall of the hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3184.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she wept and groaned bitterly.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3187.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as she wept I heard a stir without the hut,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3190.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and the light in the doorway was darkened.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3193.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I looked round to see who it was,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3195.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|then fell upon the ground in salutation,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3198.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|mother of the king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3199.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Mother of the Heavens,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_32.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|your name became great among the people of the Zulu,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3200.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that same lady to whom my mother had refused the milk.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3204.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Greeting, Mopo,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3205.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|she answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3206.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Is it because the sorrow of women is upon her?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3209.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|mother of a king,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3210.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|because this man,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3211.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|who is my brother,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3213.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|has come from him who is my lord and thy son,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3216.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|to murder that which shall be born of me.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3218.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|O thou whose breasts have given suck, plead for me!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_322.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the ideal would probably not be a low one;
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3222.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Thy son was not slain at birth.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3225.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Mother of the Zulu.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3226.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Yet may his child be otherwise, Mother of the Heavens!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3229.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Think, thou hast no grandson to comfort thee in thy age.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3233.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|The king, our lord, lives in war.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3235.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|He too may die, and what then?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3237.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Has the king no brothers?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3239.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|They are not of thy flesh, mother.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3241.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|thou dost not hearken!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3243.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then as a woman to woman I plead with thee.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3246.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Save my child or slay me with my child!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3249.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"How may this be done, Mopo?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_325.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|It only remains to the writer to express his regret that this story is not more varied in its hue.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3251.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and even reeds have ears,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3253.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"Are there then no other new-born babes in Zululand?"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3256.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|sitting up and speaking in a whisper like the hiss of a snake.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3260.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Listen, Mopo!
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3261.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Is not your wife also in labour?
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3263.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now hear me, Mother of the Heavens, and, my brother, hear me also.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3267.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Do not think to play with me in this matter.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3270.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|For I will tell the king that you came to me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3272.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then Unandi spoke.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3274.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and swear that you will be faithful to me in this secret,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3277.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|as I swear to you.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3279.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|and then in reward you shall be the greatest of the people,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3282.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|the king's voice,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3284.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|whisperer in the king's ear.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3285.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"I swear, Mother of the Heavens,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3287.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I answered.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3288.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|"It is well, my brother,"
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3290.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Now go and do that which must be done swiftly,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3293.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|for my sorrow is upon me.
