/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3356.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I said fiercely.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3358.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|And she gave me the body.
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3360.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Then I took him and wrapped him up in my bundle of medicines,
