/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3417.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|Mother of the Heavens,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3419.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|I have done your wish,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3420.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|but know that before all is finished this deed shall bring about the death of many.
