/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3431.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|But now ill-fortune found me,
/mnt/data/home/aa2249/FYP/HiFi-TTS/1hour/6097_3433.wav|HiFi_Speaker|en|that is the royal house, my father.
